verses.verse: To the <S%H5329>chief<s%> <S%H5329>Musician,<s%> A Psalm of <S%H1732>David.<s%> The <S%H5036>fool<s%> has <S%H559>said<s%> in his <S%H3820>heart,<s%> There is <S%H369>no<s%> <S%H430>God.<s%> They are <S%H7843>corrupt,<s%> they have done <S%H8581>abominable<s%> <S%H5949>works,<s%> there is <S%H369>none<s%> that <S%H6213>does<s%> <S%H2896>good.<s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H8259>looked<s%> down from <S%H8064>heaven<s%> on the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H120>men,<s%> to <S%H7200>see<s%> if there were any that did <S%H7919>understand,<s%> and <S%H1875>seek<s%> <S%H430>God.<s%>

They are <S%H3605>all<s%> <S%H5493>gone<s%> <S%H5493>aside,<s%> they are all <S%H3162>together<s%> <S%H444>become<s%> <S%H444>filthy:<s%> there is <S%H369>none<s%> that <S%H6213>does<s%> <S%H2896>good,<s%> no, not <S%H259>one.<s%>

Have <S%H3605>all<s%> the <S%H6466>workers<s%> of <S%H205>iniquity<s%> <S%H3808>no<s%> <S%H3045>knowledge?<s%> who <S%H398>eat<s%> up my <S%H5971>people<s%> as they <S%H398>eat<s%> <S%H3899>bread,<s%> and <S%H7121>call<s%> not on the <S%H3068>LORD.<s%>
<S%H8033>There<s%> were they in <S%H6343>great<s%> <S%H6342>fear:<s%> for <S%H430>God<s%> is in the <S%H1755>generation<s%> of the <S%H6662>righteous.<s%>
You have <S%H954>shamed<s%> the <S%H6098>counsel<s%> of the <S%H6041>poor,<s%> <S%H3588>because<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> is his <S%H4268>refuge.<s%>

Oh that the <S%H3444>salvation<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> were come out of <S%H6726>Zion!<s%> when the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H7725>brings<s%> <S%H7725>back<s%> the <S%H7622>captivity<s%> of his <S%H5971>people,<s%> <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> shall <S%H1523>rejoice,<s%> and <S%H3478>Israel<s%> shall be <S%H8056>glad.<s%>
